title: Ep 264 Curzio’s Weekly Q&A
itunes:title: Curzio’s Weekly Q&A
description:
Today we’re going to try something new…
 
Some many of you have emailed in questions that I’ve decided break this out as a new weekly segment and answer them here.
 
Today I’m going to go over some of my best and some of my worst ideas.
 
Email me at  with your questions and I’ll do my best to get to as many as possible
 
    
Hope you enjoy.
